Vista Chemical Co said it plans to filea registration statement with the Securities and ExchangeCommission in early covering the sale of about 4.5 mln sharesof its common stock to the public.    The shares will be sold by institutional investors whopartially financed the company upon its formation in 1984 andby the trustee of its savings and investment plan on behalf ofemployee participants.    None of the shares will be sold by the company, it said. Reuter&#3;